 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/104440/', '', 'Golimumab, Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Canakinumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Methotrexate, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, More', '', 1767369485);
